Package: xsetroot
Section: utils
Architecture: ARCH
Priority: optional
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: set root window background to a given pattern or color 
 This package provides xsetroot, a utility used to set
 your root window's background to a given pattern or 
 color.

